title: The Night Canelo RUINED An Incredible Career
author: Motivedia - Boxing
description:
Canelo vs Plant is tonight! 
And what better way for Boxing fans to prepare, than to look back at one of the most dominant displays of Saul Alvarez’ illustrious career. 
Here we take a look back to a night where two of the sports heaviest hitters met head on.. And a night where Canelo, on the comeback from his only loss, needed a destructive victory more than ever before.
